# Design System Documentation

> **AI Lead Intelligence Platform** - A comprehensive guide for maintaining consistent UI/UX across all features

---

## üé® Overview

This design system is built on **shadcn/ui** components with **Tailwind CSS v4**, featuring a modern dark-first theme with OKLCH color space for better color perception and consistency.

---

## üåà Color System

### Color Philosophy
- **Primary Color Space**: OKLCH (Oklab Lightness Chroma Hue)
- **Default Theme**: Dark mode
- **Theme Support**: Light and Dark modes with system preference detection

### Semantic Color Tokens

#### Core Colors

| Token | Light Mode | Dark Mode | Usage |
|-------|-----------|-----------|-------|
| `background` | `oklch(1 0 0)` | `oklch(0.1 0.03 260)` | Main background color (Deep Navy in dark) |
| `foreground` | `oklch(0.145 0 0)` | `oklch(0.985 0 0)` | Primary text color |
| `primary` | `oklch(0.55 0.2 260)` | `oklch(0.6 0.18 250)` | Brand color (Bright Blue/Violet) |
| `primary-foreground` | `oklch(0.985 0 0)` | `oklch(0.985 0 0)` | Text on primary background |
| `secondary` | `oklch(0.97 0 0)` | `oklch(0.2 0.05 260)` | Secondary actions |
| `muted` | `oklch(0.97 0 0)` | `oklch(0.2 0.05 260)` | Muted backgrounds |
| `muted-foreground` | `oklch(0.556 0 0)` | `oklch(0.7 0 0)` | Muted text |
| `accent` | `oklch(0.97 0 0)` | `oklch(0.2 0.05 260)` | Accent elements |
| `destructive` | `oklch(0.577 0.245 27.325)` | `oklch(0.4 0.2 25)` | Error/delete actions |
| `border` | `oklch(0.922 0 0)` | `oklch(0.2 0.05 260)` | Border color |
| `input` | `oklch(0.922 0 0)` | `oklch(0.2 0.05 260)` | Input borders |
| `ring` | `oklch(0.55 0.2 260)` | `oklch(0.6 0.18 250)` | Focus rings |

#### Card & Surface Colors

| Token | Light Mode | Dark Mode | Usage |
|-------|-----------|-----------|-------|
| `card` | `oklch(1 0 0)` | `oklch(0.13 0.03 260)` | Card backgrounds |
| `card-foreground` | `oklch(0.145 0 0)` | `oklch(0.985 0 0)` | Text on cards |
| `popover` | `oklch(1 0 0)` | `oklch(0.13 0.03 260)` | Popover backgrounds |
| `popover-foreground` | `oklch(0.145 0 0)` | `oklch(0.985 0 0)` | Text on popovers |

### Using Colors in Components

```tsx
// ‚úÖ Correct - Use semantic tokens
<div className="bg-background text-foreground">
<div className="bg-card border border-border">
<div className="bg-primary text-primary-foreground">

// ‚ùå Avoid - Hard-coded colors
<div className="bg-blue-500 text-white">
<div className="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700">
```

### Opacity Modifiers

Use opacity modifiers for subtle backgrounds and overlays:

```tsx
// Subtle backgrounds
<div className="bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20">

// Glassmorphism effect
<div className="bg-background/60 backdrop-blur-lg border border-border/50">

// Or use the utility class
<div className="glass">
```

