## üìê Layout System

### Container Pattern

All pages should use the container pattern for consistent spacing:

```tsx
<div className="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-{size}">
  {/* Content */}
</div>
```

**Container Sizes:**
- `max-w-3xl` - Forms, narrow content (768px)
- `max-w-5xl` - Standard pages (1024px)
- `max-w-7xl` - Wide layouts, dashboards (1280px)

### Page Structure

```tsx
export default function PageName() {
  return (
    <div className="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-7xl">
      {/* Header Card */}
      <Card className="p-6 mb-6">
        <div className="flex items-center justify-between">
          <div>
            <h1 className="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Page Title</h1>
            <p className="text-muted-foreground">
              Page description
            </p>
          </div>
          <div className="flex gap-3">
            {/* Action buttons */}
          </div>
        </div>
      </Card>

      {/* Main Content */}
      {/* ... */}
    </div>
  );
}
```

